'''''Stories of Our Lives'''''ni [[Kenya|film yo muri Kenya]], yasohotse muri 2014<ref>Stories of Our Lives: Kenyan Queer Narratives, Second Edition (2020) — The Nest Collective (thisisthenest.com)</ref>. Iyi filime yakozwe n’abanyamuryango ba The Nest Collective, ihuriro [[Nairobi|ry’ubuhanzi rishingiye ku mujyi wa Nairobi]], iyi filime ni anthologiya ya firime eshanu ngufi zerekana amateka y’ubuzima bwa LGBT muri [[Kenya]]. <ref>[http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/tiff-2014-review-stories-of-our-lives-anthology-film-asks-if-we-are-not-africans-what-are-we-20140905 TIFF 2014 Review: 'Stories of Our Lives' (Anthology Film Asks "If We Are Not Africans, What Are We?")]. ''[[Indiewire]]'', September 5, 2014.</ref>

