=== Ask Me Nicely ===
Kate (Kelly Gichohi), umunyeshuri wigometse wigaga mumashuri yisumbuye - ahura na Kwizera<ref>Stories Of Our Lives (2014) Movie Review from Eye for Film <nowiki>https://www.eyeforfilm.co.uk</nowiki> › review › stories-of-our-...</ref>, umunyeshuri mugenzi we muri koridoro yishuri. Batangira umubano wibanga, kugeza umuyobozi wishuri afashe ingamba zo gutandukanya bombi bahagarika Kate mwishuri<ref>Stories of | our lives - Big World Cinema <nowiki>http://bigworldcinema.com</nowiki> › production › stories-of-ou...</ref>. Mugihe yari kure yishuri, Kate atabishaka akora imibonano mpuzabitsina numuhungu mubaturanyi be<ref>Stories of Our Lives—Anthology Film (2014) - Jim Chuchu <nowiki>https://www.jimchuchu.com</nowiki> › sool</ref>. Agarutse, Kate abwira Kwizera kubyerekeye guhura numuhungu. Ibi birakaza Kwizera, biganisha ku kurangiza umubano wabo<ref>Stories of our lives - KWA films <nowiki>https://www.kwafilms.com</nowiki> › film › st...</ref>.

=== Run ===
Nyuma yo kugirana amasezerano n’ubucuruzi n’uwigana disiki(disc duplicator), Patrick (Paul Ogola) yaguye ku kabari kabo bahuje igitsina ubwo yagendanaga ninshuti ye magara, Kama. Kama agaragaza imyumvire mibi kubyerekeye akabari uko banyuze hejuru. Nyuma Patrick yaje gusubira muri club ijoro ryose, yizeye ko ntawe uzabimenya. Kama yerekana Patrick avuye mu kabari, kandi bafite guhangana gukabije . Patrick yahunze kugira ngo ahunge urugamba<ref>Kenyan Film Board Bans TIFF Film 'Stories Of Our Lives' <nowiki>https://www.indiewire.com</nowiki> › 2014/10 › kenyan-film-boar...</ref>.

=== Athman ===
Abakozi bo mu mirima Ray na Athman babaye inshuti magara imyaka myinshi. Kubabazwa nubusabane bwa Athman nubusabane na Fiona mushya, Ray yagiranye ikiganiro kibi na Athman kubyerekeye umubano wabo. Athman yongeye gushimangira ko adashishikajwe n'imibonano mpuzabitsina na Ray. Biyunze, noneho Ray abaza Athman niba ashobora kumusoma. Umukinnyi yatunguwe nikibazo aragenda, ntibyoroshye. Bombi bongera kwiyunga bukeye, ariko Ray ahitamo kuva mu murima<ref>Jim Chuchu, director. Stories of Our Lives. 2014. 60 minutes ... <nowiki>https://www.cambridge.org</nowiki> › african-studies-review › article</ref>.

=== Duet ===
Jeff (Mugambi Nthiga), umushakashatsi wasuye u [[Bwongereza]] mu nama - aha akazi umuherekeza Roman mu gihe cy'isaha imwe mu cyumba cye cya hoteri. Roman (Louis Brooke) arahagera, yumva impungenge za Jeff, agerageza kumutuza. Jeff abaza niba bashobora kuvuga bike mbere yo kwishora mubikorwa byose. Bombi baricara bakaganira kubyerekeye isano iri hagati yubwoko . Roman noneho aha Jeff massage, bigatuma Jeff adahangayika.<ref>Stories of Our Lives by Nest Collective - Online Screening <nowiki>https://contemporaryand.com</nowiki> › Events</ref>

=== Each Night I Dream ===
Liz (Rose Njenga), yerekana gahunda zidasanzwe zo guhunga we na mugenzi we Achi mugihe abadepite baho bakangisha kubahiriza amategeko arwanya abaryamana bahuje ibitsina<ref>Kenyan film tells stories of LGBT lives | Al Jazeera America <nowiki>http://america.aljazeera.com</nowiki> › blogs › scrutineer › keny...</ref>.

== Umusaruro ==
''Stories of Our Lives'' Yatangiye nkumushinga winyandiko na Nest Collective. Iri tsinda ryazengurutse [[Kenya]], rifata amajwi yabajijwe n'abantu bavuga ko ari LGBTIQ. Iyandikwa ryabaye ishingiro rya firime vignettes. <ref name="variety">[https://variety.com/2014/film/festivals/stores-of-our-lives-lgbt-kenya-community1201299178-1201299178/ ‘Stories of Our Lives’ Sheds Light on Kenya’s Gay Community]. ''[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]'', September 5, 2014.</ref> 15,000 y’amadorali yavuye muri Uhai / EASHRI - ikigega cy’uburenganzira bw’imibonano mpuzabitsina muri Afurika y’iburasirazuba gifite icyicaro i [[Nairobi]], muri [[Kenya]] - kikaba cyarafashwe amashusho n’itsinda mu gihe cy’amezi umunani hakoreshejwe kamera imwe ya Canon DSLR. <ref name="xtra">[https://www.dailyxtra.com/kenyan-filmmakers-come-out-ahead-of-tiff-premiere-63448 "Kenyan filmmakers ‘come out’ ahead of TIFF premiere"]. ''[[Xtra!]]'', September 5, 2014.</ref> <ref>[http://www.tiff.net/festivals/thefestival/programmes/discovery/stories-of-our-lives Stories of Our Lives]. ''TIFF.net'', November 19, 2014.</ref>
